translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_994afe76:
    # "Sarah drafted her orders and handed them down."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_eaa69cc9:
    # "From her hands, to her commanders, to the officers and soon down to every last man and woman in her army."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_72c1c4fa:
    # "The warcamp swelled with excitement. The eagerness of soldiers too long denied a battle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_66a55ece:
    # "Perhaps only the old knew of the carnage to come, but few soldiers lived to be old."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_ffb98eb5:
    # "By early next morning, the army had completed its preparations and begun to march."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_090a9d90:
    # "Riding near the lead, Sarah surveyed her army, trying to coax out any weakness she had perhaps missed."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_3cf53a05:
    # "The snow slowed them down, but not by as much as she had feared."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_81879fbb:
    # "Many of the soldiers in her army were Rosannan natives, familiar with the hard winters."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_e59e06d7:
    # "As they marched, they soon found themselves coming upon the crossroad."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_22575e1a:
    # "One part, poorly maintained, branched off into the Hinterlands. The main road, however, continued on to the city of Calshure."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_23b7e630:
    # "Seeing the quality of the road, Sarah was happy with the decision she had made."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_704cd07e:
    # "Sarah rode near the center of her army, quickly able to react to any problems encountered by the vanguard or the rear of the column."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_badd2521:
    # "But the main road was well maintained, and so even with the heavy snowfall of the last few days, her army found little obstacle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_1ab90ae2:
    # "The wagons, heavy with cargo and equipment, rolled along on the solid stone."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_fa788dfe:
    # "All around her, Sarah found her men in good spirits, laughing among themselves, at times even breaking out into song."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_58c84437:
    # "This too was part of their youth. Their inexperience."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_c5694b16:
    # "They did not know war, and so they did not fear it the way they should."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_f1627ffd:
    # "As her army marched along, making solid progress on the first day, Sarah could not help but shake this thought."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_7da6f474:
    # "Her army, for the most part, was made up out of Rosannan natives."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_f555cdc6:
    # "Then there were the Legions that Gilead had offered."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_774795ec:
    # "They marched in stoic unison. Perfectly trained. Perfectly armed."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_5c6d5053:
    # "Almost the ideal image of what an army should be."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_3c69f81f:
    # "And there were her mercenaries. What they perhaps lacked in discipline they made up in experience."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_73326cc7:
    # "Each was seasoned by several campaigns, and each knew what war actually meant."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_87a62311:
    # "Out of all of them, it was her own people that she feared for."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_c49a225c:
    # "The Rosannan people were mostly farmers, dreaming of living easy lives with good harvests."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_c781a9d1:
    # "They were not born into war."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_2a3a6a4a:
    # "Not the way a Tribesman was."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_53ea95f8:
    # "Tribesmen were raised from childhood to fight."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_21328b9a:
    # "By the time they were adults, most had already served in at least two campaigns."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_73949062:
    # "Not only were they experienced, their culture was also different."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_77470704:
    # "Rosannans feared death, but the Tribesmen almost yearned for it."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_0c290b91:
    # "The greatest pride for a Tribesmen was a good death, and so they plunged themselves into battle with no fear."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_a85fe639:
    # "For the greatest danger to themselves was victory or earning eternal glory."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_75f36042:
    # "Her only advantage was that going off most reports was that the Tribesmen army was significantly smaller than her army."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_3ee91b0d:
    # "But Sarah also knew wars were decided by more than just numbers."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_52ca461e:
    # "In her stomach, she felt the dread grow as they marched on the city of Calshure."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_d3bbcae3:
    # "Marching along the main road, they progressed much faster than Sarah had even dared to hope."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_bd9f2f86:
    # "In under two days, they reached the city of Calshure."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_8b795ed1:
    # "She spotted it the moment it crossed over the horizon, a plume of smoke rising up from it."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_2b5e16aa:
    # "The harsh grey of the city walls stood in sharp contrast to the snow."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_ed5f7e87:
    # "Her army swiftly closed the distance."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_293af4c6:
    # "One of the scouts that had been send ahead to investigate the city, rode to meet her."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_5fc4c1bc:
    # "Scout" "Commander!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_406066de:
    # "Sarah turned to face the scout."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_c10edc01:
    # s "Report?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_f83e9a67:
    # "Scout" "The city is in the hands of the Tribesmen."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_e3e29fc2:
    # "Scout" "A regiment of Tribesmen soldiers is in control of they city, and they're out in force."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_40aa162e:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_09b8d5b9:
    # "A regiment wasn't too bad in terms of numbers. Still, they had the advantage of holding the city walls."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_d8ab4f04:
    # "Scout" "They've shut the gates to the city and they've drafted the city militia to help secure the fortifications."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_30a6abf9:
    # "Sarah frowned."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_56f6efc5:
    # "The town militia likely had little love for the Tribesmen, but they were inside, trapped with them."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_4bf2213e:
    # "They had spend the last few years learning to listen obediently, or suffer the consequences."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_39197cb4:
    # "Hell, some of the younger soldiers in the militia might have lived most of their young adult lives knowing nothing but Tribe rule."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_0a156f4f:
    # "Sarah knew they would be loyal to her, but only if she took the city."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_34c4351a:
    # "Before, they would defend it. Causing her to lose precious soldiers fighting her own people."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_1be074bf:
    # s "Anything else?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_f0a3a8a9:
    # "The scout nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_d7badff9:
    # "Scout" "Yes, commander...I..."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_683cabef:
    # s "Just say it."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_7ed783b6:
    # "Scout" "I...approached the city gates as close as I dared."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_7c507643:
    # "Scout" "When I finally turned to leave, I heard a voice call out to me."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_fa69b9ed:
    # s "A voice?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_f0a3a8a9_1:
    # "The scout nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_b2f59333:
    # "Scout" "It was a Tribesman soldier. He identified himself as the leader of the regiment."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_58ec3148:
    # s "What did he say?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_8f823a64:
    # "Scout" "He...requested a meeting with you."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_8dd9efc9:
    # s "A meeting?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_fd7d8bc4:
    # s "Did he say what about?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_4b631abd:
    # "The scout shook his head."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_405ab93a:
    # "Scout" "No, only that he would ride out by sunset to meet you on the open field outside of Calshure."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_3ff6393d:
    # "Scout" "And that if you wanted to meet, to be there."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_40aa162e_1:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_8efadb58:
    # s "Thank you, that's all. Good work."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_ccd719e6:
    # "The scout saluted her and rode off again."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_fcb4bbf7:
    # "Finally, her army settled outside of Calshure, as close as they could manage without falling into the range of archers."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_3f6c1732:
    # "The city was so close, Sarah imagined she could ride out to it in only a few minutes."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_3d65c7f5:
    # "So close, yet with its walls up and gates shut, it might as well be a different world."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_7d0471d0:
    # "She had no doubt she could siege Calshure. Take the city by force."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_f2c1b115:
    # "But perhaps there was value in meeting the Tribesman. Perhaps there was a different way to resolve this."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_6f54e8fd:
    # "Then again, what if it was just distraction? Intended to delay her advance. Delay a siege by a few more days."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_04a510a8:
    # "Their only real hope was to wait for reinforcements from the main Tribal army, stationed in the Capital. More than a few days away still."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen6Calshure_335c046b:
    # "Sarah considered her options."
    ""

